<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/414713-on-pages-212-213-she-talks-about-why-we">. On pages 212-213 she talks about why we eat the way we do in America. Do you agree
with her assessment that it isn’t about spending more time or more money? Explain
how her solution of everyone knowing how to cook well and have access to good ingredients could be implemented.</a>
</div>
